Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 嘿嘿 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真高兴啊 第二张签名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 哇~ 哇~
